{"tid":612609,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Mac mini停產，新產品Mac Air準備接棒","createTime":"2018-04-01T03:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T06:02:19.000Z","uid":294,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c55379624226606b7e62f07fbcaf8dea301ebb14","tid":612609,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.cultofmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Mac-Air-1000x500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cultofmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F03%2FMac-Air-1000x500.jpg&h=e38a72f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經有 4年沒有更新的 Mac mini 將在今天正式走入歷史，取而代之的是 Apple 今日發表的新產品：Mac Air。 <br />\nMac Air 號稱世界最輕薄桌上型電腦，重量僅 590 克，比原本的 Mac mini 還要輕 52%，體積比一台 11 吋的 MacBook Air 對折後還要再小（因為沒有鍵盤、螢幕、電池）。Mac Air 全面採用 SSD，搭配 Iris Pro 顯示晶片，升級為 Thunderbolt 2，支援 4K 螢幕。美國地區預計 4/15 出貨，台灣地區可能要等到六月。 <br />\n規格與售價： <br />\nMac Air / i5 2.6 雙核 / 8GB RAM / 256GB SSD / Iris Pro / NT$ 19,400 (約HK$ 5,000) <br />\nMac Air / i7 2.6 四核 / 16GB RAM / 512GB SSD / Iris Pro / NT$ 25,900 (約HK$ 6,500) <br />\n<br />\nApple 官方透過新聞稿表示： <br />\n身為一家全球性的頂尖企業，我們必須在人類語言上樹立良好的典範。在此之前，我們發現許多用戶竟然擅自把 MacBook Air 縮寫成 Mac Air，更荒謬的是，大多數的用戶根本搞不清楚 MacBook Pro 和 Mac Pro 是兩個完全不同的東西，並且常常把他們混為一談，這令我們的開發團隊非常沮喪。 <br />\n因此，為了杜絕這個亂象，我們推出了 Mac Air，它將會為桌上型電腦市場帶來巨大的革命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7c8559b6fb921468a60e2f84adfe609920324f","tid":612609,"uid":28550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:09:10.000Z","msg":"4月1......."},{"pid":"b5447af4d5ad20e75aadeb693f0a95da470de1dc","tid":612609,"uid":37338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:10:27.000Z","msg":"Fake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ba122db0458f56e54e36ec5b6dbf87750191df","tid":612609,"uid":143206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765767f1038e81cdfd1718708b94d6edc91d1ff9","tid":612609,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"又loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41756f51ed14429a318e40975bb0806b761f4e6","tid":612609,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:26:35.000Z","msg":"其實Mac mini真正後繼機係垃圾筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd0336f36d05724bf3190b0f29f498813ff0818","tid":612609,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"marbook air其實仲點會出<br />\n<br />\nmacbook 12&quot;仲細過macbook air<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cae12f82c4591f20acafb59bbf1bb66db4c0a0","tid":612609,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"呢個價，一望就知fake"},{"pid":"4481f27d62a845168989b5edbd221f6e68003773","tid":612609,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"已經睇到Mac air=April fool"},{"pid":"f40af37663c7e8154a022ce6d5b82b3a7bd41fd3","tid":612609,"uid":1001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:02:19.000Z","msg":"個價係幾多年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}